I have been doing this for 2 years now but have finally decided to share here on Instagram incase you or someone you know may need this service for a loved one. 

Mortuary Makeup: It is my utmost honor to serve as a mortuary makeup artist for your loved one. There is a difference in makeup artistry between a mortician and a professional makeup artist. I witnessed this first hand after the viewing of my Father. At that moment I realized I could do this and do it better. 

I would love the opportunity to help assist in the funeral arrangements. I also offer hair styling and dressing. I request that you provide a photo of your deceased loved one so I can plan accordingly.  I will create an environment that is absolutely safe and calm to help your loved one genuinely “rest in peace”.
